// File 2: SingleBlogPage.js import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import './BlogPage.css'; const SingleBlogPage = ({ match }) => { const blogId = parseInt(match.params.id); const blogData = [ { id: 1, title: "Spring Fashion Trends 2023", excerpt: "Discover the hottest fashion trends for spring 2023 that will transform your wardrobe", content: `

Spring 2023 brings a refreshing mix of bold colors, innovative textures, and nostalgic silhouettes. This season, fashion is all about self-expression and embracing individuality.

One of the standout trends is the return of vibrant pastels. From soft lavender to mint green, these hues are appearing in everything from tailored suits to flowing dresses. Designers are encouraging us to experiment with color in unexpected ways.

Another significant trend is the emphasis on sustainable materials. Many brands are introducing pieces made from recycled fabrics and innovative eco-friendly materials, proving that style and sustainability can coexist beautifully.

Key Trends to Try:

  • Oversized blazers with strong shoulders
  • Sheer fabrics layered over minimalist pieces
  • Utility details on dresses and separates
  • Statement accessories in bold, geometric shapes

Whether you're refreshing your entire wardrobe or just adding a few key pieces, these trends offer plenty of inspiration for creating looks that feel both current and uniquely you.
